name: Diana Moyer
description:
I’m cheerful, reliable, open, easygoing, responsible,open and kind person, very understanding.
Regarding the type of Companion I desire,Trust and confidence. It’s relatively simple Race, ethnicity and physical appearance in general is not the problem. My interest is in a good personality and sense of humor for I need someone to lift my spirits. I don’t care about age because I think age is just a number because maturity is the capacity to endure uncertainty .
